const buttonStyle = {
    background: 'transparent',
    border: 'none',
    boxShadow: 'none',
    outline: 'none',
    width: '16.6%',
    height: '20%'
}

const sectionStyle = {
    width: '100%',
    height: '100%',
    display: 'inline-block',
    verticalAlign: 'top',
    whiteSpace: 'normal'
}

const slideContainer = {
    overflow: 'hidden',
    width: '210px',
    whiteSpace: 'nowrap',
    display: 'inline-block',
    position: 'sticki',
    bottom: '50px',
    transform: '',

}

const containerStyle = {
    position: 'absolute',
    //display: 'inline-block',
    transform: 'translate(-150px ,-185px)',
    width: '250px',
    height: '130px',
    background: 'white',
    boxSizing: 'content-box',
    padding: '5px',
}

const sliderNavigationButton = {
    ...buttonStyle,
    display: 'inline-block',
    width: '20px',
    height: '100%',
    top: '50%',
    verticalAlign: 'top'
}

const iconStyle = {
    transform: 'translateX(-25%)',
}
